@startuml contacts-state
' Context: contacts
' SDD: PROM-PERSONAL-CONTACTS, SYS-CONTACTS
' Revision: 2026-07-18

title Contacts — ContactsController state machine

state Loading : isLoading = true
state Ready : contacts in memory\nisLoading = false

[*] --> Loading : LoadContacts\n[constructor]

Loading --> Ready : ContactsLoaded
Loading --> Ready : ContactsLoadFailed\n[error set]

Ready --> Ready : SetSearchQuery\n/ filteredContacts
Ready --> Ready : AddInternalContact\n/ reload LoadContacts
Ready --> Ready : AddExternalContact\n/ reload LoadContacts
Ready --> Ready : RemoveInternalContact\n/ reload LoadContacts

note right of Ready
  Ricerca lista: filtro locale
  (filterByQuery), non cambia stato.
  Sheet aggiunta: SearchProfiles
  è UI locale nel bottom sheet.
end note

@enduml
